data.description:
NEW ROOF prior to closing. Welcome to your dream oasis in the heart of Melbourne! This stunning POOL home has been meticulously renovated to blend modern luxury with timeless charm, offering the perfect blend of comfort and style. Nestled in a prime location, this property boasts a spacious backyard that's an entertainer's paradise.

Newer HVAC system, newer paint, all luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout (no carpet), and oversized screened lanai.

With mature landscaping and plenty of green space, this backyard is a canvas for your imagination. Create your own garden oasis, set up a play area, or simply enjoy the tranquility of your own private sanctuary.

Situated in a sought-after neighborhood, you'll have easy access to Melbourne's finest dining shopping, and entertainment options. Its central location makes commuting is a breeze
